text: Francyne Aparecida Jacintho (born 16 July 1992) is a Brazilian volleyball player who has represented her country in world championships. She is a member of the Brazil women's national volleyball team. She was part of the Brazil national indoor volleyball team at the 2010 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup, and 2016 Montreux Volley Masters.
